invalid type: string "HDFC Mutual Fund - Investor Service Portal\n\n1. Download CAS (Consolidated Account Statement):\nVisit cams/kfintech portals. Steps: PAN + Email -> Statement Type -> Custom Period -> Email sent.\n\n2. Update Bank Mandate:\nLogin to HDFC MF Online -> Profile -> Bank Details -> Add/Update Mandate. Or visit any registrar office (CAMS) with a cancelled cheque and a Request Form.˙